items.headline: Visit the Animal OC Wiki
items.desc: At the Animal OC Wiki you can post about your animal characters. This includes regular animals, anthros, reptiles, birds, mammals, even bugs if you want. You can help others improve their own characters and also get help with your own characters. Be sure to read the rules before contributing. The Animal OC Wiki is a safe place for anyone interested to join.
